title: Dido - Maximum Dido - The Unauthorised Biography Of Dido
description:
Dido - Maximum Dido - The Unauthorised Biography Of Dido


Maximum Dido is a spoken word audio-biography CD that tells the full story of this incredible performer. The biography benefits from freshly researched information throughout, and includes exclusive interviews with the artist herself, to give the listener a stunning level of insight into the subject.
